{{!-- Phase 12: Warranty Cert Template (Vietnamese) --}}
<div class="classic-header" style="margin-bottom: 30pt;">
  <div class="classic-header__republic-line">{{t "republic_header"}}</div>
  <div class="classic-header__motto">{{t "independence_motto"}}</div>
  <div class="classic-header__dash">-----------------</div>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40pt;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 24pt; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; color: #1e3a8a; margin-bottom: 8pt;">{{t "document_title_warranty_cert"}}</h1>
  <div style="font-size: 12pt; color: #4b5563;">{{t "doc_number"}}: BH-{{contract.contractNo}}/{{date generatedAt "year"}}</div>
</div>

<main class="classic-body">
  <div style="text-align: center; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 30pt;">
    <p>{{t "warranty_cert_statement" contractNo=contract.contractNo}}</p>
  </div>

  <h3 style="margin-top: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase;">{{t "delivery_sender"}} ({{t "party_b"}})</h3>
  <table class="classic-parties" width="100%">
    <tr>
      <th>Tên công ty:</th>
      <td><strong>{{company.name}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>{{t "address"}}:</th>
      <td>{{company.address}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>Hotline:</th>
      <td><strong>{{company.phone}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>Hỗ trợ kỹ thuật:</th>
      <td>{{company.email}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h3 style="margin-top: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase;">ĐƠN VỊ THỤ HƯỞNG ({{t "party_a"}})</h3>
  <table class="classic-parties" width="100%">
    <tr>
      <th>Tên công ty:</th>
      <td><strong>{{customer.name}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>{{t "address"}}:</th>
      <td>{{customer.address}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>Hệ thống:</th>
      <td><strong>{{project.name}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h3 style="margin-top: 20pt; border-bottom: 2pt solid #1e3a8a; padding-bottom: 4pt; display: inline-block;">I. {{t "warranty_period"}}</h3>
  <div style="margin-top: 10pt; padding-left: 12pt;">
    <p><strong>Thời gian:</strong> <span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #b91c1c; font-weight: bold;">{{warrantyPeriodMonths}} THÁNG</span></p>
    <p><strong>{{t "warranty_start_date"}}:</strong> {{date contract.expectedEndDate "long"}}</p>
    <p><strong>{{t "warranty_end_date"}}:</strong> {{date warrantyEndDate "long"}}</p>
  </div>

  <h3 style="margin-top: 20pt; border-bottom: 2pt solid #1e3a8a; padding-bottom: 4pt; display: inline-block;">II. {{t "warranty_conditions"}}</h3>
  <div style="margin-top: 10pt; padding-left: 12pt; text-align: justify;">
    <p>{{t "warranty_conditions_desc"}}</p>
    <ul style="margin-top: 8pt;">
      <li>Thời gian tiếp nhận sự cố: 24/7 qua Hotline.</li>
      <li>Thời gian xử lý: Tối đa 48h làm việc kể từ khi xác nhận lỗi.</li>
      <li>Mọi yêu cầu hỗ trợ vui lòng sử dụng Email định danh hoặc số điện thoại đã đăng ký.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="avoid-break" style="margin-top: 50pt;">
    <div class="signature-grid classic-signature">
      <div class="signature-col text-center" style="width: 100%;">
        <div class="signature-block__label"><strong>ĐẠI DIỆN {{company.name}}</strong></div>
        <div style="height: 100pt;">
          <div class="classic-stamp" style="margin-top: -10pt;">ĐÓNG DẤU & KÝ TÊN</div>
        </div>
        <div style="font-weight: bold;">{{company.representative}}</div>
        <div style="font-size: 11pt; color: #4b5563;">{{company.representativeTitle}}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

{{> footer-page}}
